<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<text id="02-output-contract" title="Product-Led Growth (PM Angle) Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema draft-07 for the spec artefact this methodology produces, with valid and invalid examples plus forbidden patterns.</summary>

  <section title="Schema (JSON Schema draft-07)">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/product-led-growth.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": [
    "product_id",
    "aha_moment",
    "pql_criteria",
    "activation_cohort_tracked",
    "expansion_owner",
    "experiment_throttle"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "product_id": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "aha_moment": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": [
        "event_sequence",
        "max_minutes_from_signup"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "event_sequence": {
          "type": "array",
          "minItems": 1,
          "items": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        },
        "max_minutes_from_signup": {
          "type": "integer",
          "maximum": 10,
          "minimum": 1
        }
      }
    },
    "pql_criteria": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": [
        "events",
        "frequency",
        "account_shape"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "events": {
          "type": "array",
          "minItems": 1,
          "items": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        },
        "frequency": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "account_shape": {
          "type": "string"
        }
      }
    },
    "activation_cohort_tracked": {
      "const": true
    },
    "expansion_owner": {
      "enum": [
        "pm",
        "growth-pm",
        "pmm"
      ]
    },
    "experiment_throttle": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": [
        "max_concurrent_per_step"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "max_concurrent_per_step": {
          "type": "integer",
          "maximum": 2,
          "minimum": 0
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": true
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "product_id": "acme-api",
  "aha_moment": {
    "event_sequence": [
      "api_key_created",
      "api_call_succeeded"
    ],
    "max_minutes_from_signup": 8
  },
  "pql_criteria": {
    "events": [
      "api_call_succeeded"
    ],
    "frequency": ">=10/week",
    "account_shape": "company_size > 10"
  },
  "activation_cohort_tracked": true,
  "expansion_owner": "pm",
  "experiment_throttle": {
    "max_concurrent_per_step": 2
  }
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "product_id": "p1",
  "aha_moment": {
    "event_sequence": [],
    "max_minutes_from_signup": 30
  },
  "pql_criteria": {
    "events": []
  },
  "activation_cohort_tracked": false,
  "expansion_owner": "sales",
  "experiment_throttle": {
    "max_concurrent_per_step": 5
  }
}
]]></code>
    <note>aha event_sequence empty; max minutes &gt; 10; pql events empty + missing frequency/account_shape; activation_cohort_tracked false; expansion_owner sales; throttle exceeds 2.</note>
  </example>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item>aha_moment.max_minutes_from_signup &gt; 10 (not aha by definition).</item>
      <item>activation_cohort_tracked = false (signup-cohort tracking forbidden).</item>
      <item>expansion_owner outside {pm, growth-pm, pmm} (handed to sales).</item>
      <item>experiment_throttle.max_concurrent_per_step &gt; 2 (stacked experiments confound).</item>
      <item>pql_criteria.events empty (PQL undefined).</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-product-led-growth.py">Validator script enforcing this schema</reference>
</text>
